---
layout: layouts/marketing.njk
title: "Blog"
description: "Notes from building Project Budget — design decisions, release notes, and the occasional opinion on personal finance."
permalink: /blog/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<article class="container container--narrow page">
  <header class="page__header">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p class="page__subtitle">Notes from building Project Budget — design decisions, release notes, and the occasional opinion on personal finance.</p>
  </header>

  {% if collections.posts and collections.posts.length %}
    <ol class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
        <li class="post-list__item">
          <p class="post-list__meta">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            {% if post.data.tag %} &middot; {{ post.data.tag }}{% endif %}
          </p>
          <h2 class="post-list__title">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          {% if post.data.summary %}
            <p class="post-list__summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  {% else %}
    <p>No posts yet.</p>
  {% endif %}

  <p class="post-list__feed">
    <a href="/feed.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/atom+xml">RSS / Atom feed</a>
  </p>
</article>
